title: [FEATURE] New Icons Needed!
body:
**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**

The problem is simple: we have no icon.

**Describe the solution you'd like**

A good icon to make everyone proud.

**Describe alternatives you've considered**

Reusing SkiaSharp's icon. That is not cool. We are cool.
